Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,'Mystery Train'?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Bell Tree Express, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never thought Sherry would ride such a ridiculously conspicuous train like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but isn't it a fitting choice for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every room on that train is private.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she's trying to escape from the Kant≈ç region without us noticing, it would be a perfect way, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I just can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never expected that Sherry was hiding out in the Gunma mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bourbon, who discovered that information, had the same opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:46.27,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,He said that since it's just something she happened to tell a third party she came into contact with, it's not necessarily accurate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Sherry is riding on that train,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be the best hunting ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. With nary a stop to disembark midway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's a moving steel prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just like hunting a deer, if we just shake her with fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she'll likely expose herself to the barrel of the gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know why I deliberately leaked this information to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to keep my distance until that metal snake has returned to its hole, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm happy to hear the name 'Sherry' from you after so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was beginning to think you were showing mercy for a fellow woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who do you take me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's talk again once the hunt is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll give up on Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:56.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It won't be me who finishes her off, but Bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She mustn't be allowed to remain in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Silver Bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:16.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\c&HAAAA00\t(0,4520,\c)}Seeking comprehensive answers, he solves every mystery and code!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\t(0,1510,\c&H88AA00)}As the departure bell rings out, the shadows of the Organisation approach Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\c&H88AA00)\t(0,1580,\c)}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\t(0,1880,\c&HAA00AA)}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\c&HAA00AA\t(0,1870,\c&H0000FF)}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen a steam locomotive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, the SL appearance is just a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside it is a state-of-the-art diesel engine, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're still not better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somebody{\i0}'s germs are pretty stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why aren't you staying at home and resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could at least show thanks for the owners of the Bell Tree Express, the Suzuki Financial Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We specially reserved seats just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, unlike yours, our seats are in the luxurious first-class car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, isn't that the same first-class car that Kid announced he'd target soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a rule, this train only runs once a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but this year, Uncle Jirokichi's going to run it specially one more time to exhibit some jewel in the first-class car
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s sure to ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I decided I'd be a step ahead of him and leave a love letter to him in the train car! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt Kid would have time to steal a letter as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ky≈çgoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be pretty upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My love for Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} has nothing to do with my love for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm interested in isn't any thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the deduction quiz they always do aboard the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective! Of course I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't your dad with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He was right here a moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, And≈ç{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I take your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a valuable item my client entrusted me with, and it's quite heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, the heavy part is the solid-gold picture frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The painting's just a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appraiser had finished with it, so I'm escorting it back to my client in Nagoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? But this is the Mystery Train, destination unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you think it's headed to Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:32.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mr. Conductor... How many years have we been meeting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:39.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Anyone can easily deduce that by checking which trains have had their schedules changed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:44.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The crux of what stimulates our intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,is the mystery acted out on board this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Sumitomo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've expected no less from mystery connoisseurs like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:05.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I know I reserved my usual room on the first-class car, Carriage 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So why'd I get moved to Carriage 7?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we mentioned a few days back, we had accidentally double-booked the room, so we had to move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my favourite room, and I book it every single year the moment tickets go on sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the jackass who muscled in on my room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the 'jackass' in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, my daughter is a friend of the owners of this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:44.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you can be assured that with me on board, no matter what case awaits aboard this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, the great detective Poir≈ç Mouri,\Nshall instantly bring the truth to light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying hello to my fellow Carriage 8 passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to smoke here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's this 'Poir≈ç' thing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kogor≈ç Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody's waiting for you in front of Carriage 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They want to take a group photo before we depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this tense atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it because they realised the old man's a detective, or perhaps...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the stations are just flying past!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be almost nonstop until we reach the destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, where the final stop is located is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Nagoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look up the train schedules on the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can figure out this train's route...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was so excited to get on a Mystery Train, and this guy goes and ruins it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm interested in is the deduction quiz that's gonna take place aboard the train in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumour goes that a culprit and victim are picked from the passengers at random, and an incident occurs between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of the passengers become detectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the goal being to figure out the culprit before the train reaches its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Congratulations, you've been selected to play the role of the detective!'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'In 10 minutes, an incident will take place in Carriage 7, Room B, so please investigate!'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Weren't all the passengers supposed to be the detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carriage 7, Room B... Carriage 7, Room B...{bluesun: Carriageriage 7 Room B, Carriageriage 7 Room B...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! It's this room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come in, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, awesome! It's just like the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! You too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't much of a mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more like a game of tag...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We lost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the rooms are private, so we can't tell if they went into one of the rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time on this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, you better stay in your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deduction quiz will be announced via the speakers in each room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the case hasn't started at all yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't start for another hour, I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then what did we just witness...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be... Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should at least knock before you enter a lady's room, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Carriage 7, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? This is Carriage 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've just come here to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I miscounted the carriages...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The carriage numbers are only written on the outside of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only thing displayed on the room doors is a single alphabetic letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how'd you do on the deduction quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this room, our room, on Carriage 6?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the snacks you all were just eating are right where you left them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only moved down one carriage from Carriage 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Carriage 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Carriage 7 disappeared while the train was in motion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carriage 7 disappeared? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a guy who just got shot in Carriage 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We chased the culprit who shot him after they flew from the room, but we lost 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when we went back to Carriage 7 where the passenger who got shot was, it was Carriage 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, why didn't you immediately tell that to one of us conductors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, we thought it was part of the deduction quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please check at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carriage 7 disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the passenger who was shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should ask the conductor in each carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll be sitting in the rearmost part of the hallway in each passenger car, like I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you all just got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In compliance with the owner's specifications, the carriage numbers aren't displayed inside the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner's specifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it means that many passengers can't tell which room is theirs, and it's a lot of work for us conductors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, how may I be of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you ring the bell like that, the lamp above the room lights up and the conductor will come, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome! I wanna try it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the missing Carriage 7 comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, aren't you feeling well from the cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm fine. I've been taking medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man earlier... I got a similar feeling to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what was that burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carriage 7?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really Carriage 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carriage 7 must have reappeared while we were distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go to Room B again and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, um... Is this really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? It's Carriage 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brats like you should just go back to your room and stay out of trouble, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that conductor got confused?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe. He looks pretty sleepy to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:51.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on. Hold on... Last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} Carriage 7, Room B...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, you guys got one too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A card just like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were doing what the card said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To temporarily switch rooms with the person playing the victim role
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and confuse the detectives that would come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're amazing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone knocked on our door and when we opened it, there was an envelope on the ground, and the card inside it said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Congratulations! You've been chosen to play the role of the accomplice!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the rest was just as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'The guest playing the role of the victim in Carriage 7, Room B was waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so switch with them to help enliven the deduction quiz!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shouldn't I be the one getting angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just as the passenger who was playing the victim role and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s party were switching,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I passed through and joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the person who played the victim role is probably relaxing in our room in Carriage 8 now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then where's Uncle Kogor≈ç?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim guy told him to go to the dining car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the dining car?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted Dad to play the role of the detective who explained the answer to the deduction quiz at the end...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he asked Dad to stand by in the dining car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's nice to meet you finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that girl named 'Haibara', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to talk with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-She...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, I thought someone was peering in through the crack in the door...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I imagine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the cuisine and wine are both excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burning off the fields...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured out the disappearing corpse trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't released the deduction quiz for this journey yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I got this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}do{\i0} look like the instruction cards we usually use, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick for this journey wasn't anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess we'll have to go to Carriage 8 and ask the victim ourselves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the toilet first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel a strange presence in this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a menacing feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just you having read too many of Christie's novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:32.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This presence... isn't just one or two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, how may I be of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}? Noto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't call for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the bell just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, when I call for you, no one comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I {\i1}don't{\i0} need you, you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was some kind of trouble in the room next door, but it looks like the conductor just made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can't you do something about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about...?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a strange sound in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just sounding earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you calling me a liar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, this sound. You hear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably a mobile phone or similar that someone left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't come in! I'll find it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I want to know is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you find the mobile phone before the train set off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is! This is our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick's been found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out and explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sheesh. Don't tell me he's sleeping in our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister! Wake up and undo the chain lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's taking a nap on our sofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood coming from his forehead, it almost looks like he's really dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure it's just some sort of deduction quiz clue again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It smells like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpowder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another deduction quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall unveil the truth of this murder on the Bell Tree Express for all to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just heard from Vermouth. She confirmed that Sherry's aboard the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:00.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.57,0:24:06.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the Organisation really have come for me, aboard this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:08.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then I can't...
